repose install
==============

setup::

  $ . $TESTROOT/setup

  $ repose_chatty+=('repoq%*' 'scp%*' 'ssh%*')
  $ repose_dryrun+=('ssh%*')

  $ fake-refhost root@omg.example.org x86_64 \
  >   sles:12 \
  >   --

  $ fake-refhost root@wtf.example.org x86_64 \
  >   sles:12 \
  >   --

  $ fake-refhost root@osuse.example.org x86_64 \
  >   openSUSE:42.2 \
  >   --
